Sorry if this is the wrong section for this and thanks. :) AND IT IS AN IP CHANGER AND I NOT SURE HOW T MAKE IT NORMAL IP
(And remember people who want to give me nasty comments, I have already tried many times to make the jar, so this is why I want someone to do it for me.)
